{"tid":1433421,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【警世】近排成日發夢嘅巴絲請入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-08T13:12:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T02:04:57.000Z","uid":202770,"like":65,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"998f87541106667856a5e49049fc93721a13b271","tid":1433421,"uid":202770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:12:24.000Z","msg":"辛苦曬咁多位手足發咗咁多日夢<br />\n可能大家開始會覺得攰<br />\n有時睇連登又會開始見到多咗人係到割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到人都心灰意冷埋<br />\n<br />\n但我想話俾你地知<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地無做錯到！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n每一個天才 被大眾公認為天才 之前<br />\n都會俾身邊其他人當係癡線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但時間會證明到究竟誰是誰非！<br />\n<br />\n小弟不才，寫咗一首歌想送俾大家<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JmFmZUNy1Jk&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJmFmZUNy1Jk%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9cjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=cf3afaa1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JmFmZUNy1Jk&amp;feature=youtu.be</a> <br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n#幾大力錫都唔割 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d59d8c49f7efc3335e8d3d8f8a0640cc6f03d4","tid":1433421,"uid":98117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:12:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d386892610e29dc04e86f7e151ad07bae5f7e50","tid":1433421,"uid":202770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:13:15.000Z","msg":"無錯，又係我地兩個"},{"pid":"617792cd8cc224868b237530133d44b9ae3f50b0","tid":1433421,"uid":98117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:13:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face