plyTime":"2019-08-08T14:12:07.000Z","msg":"因為天才說的話和其他人都不一樣﹐因此人們恐懼﹐恐懼自己過去相信的會在一夕間被推翻﹐怕以後再沒有可相信的事。"},{"pid":"efed24057446fd2469c23883e5fbc0d25a2d2676","tid":1433421,"uid":202770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:12:27.000Z","msg":"「不怕、不怕﹐我們人多的是。」<br />\n<br />\n於是多數暴力每天攻擊着小眾﹐那些在大眾間的少數﹐然後把他們指認為胡言亂語的瘋子。翻騰着的輿論的海﹐這些年來淹沒過多少天才？"},{"pid":"8aef0bb24e7c00ee760dc18ccda81cd04265d9d8","tid":1433421,"uid":202770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:12:42.000Z","msg":"所以數十年後﹐這都市中的天才好像滅絕了﹐而平庸的人都在竊笑：<br />\n<br />\n「終於、終於﹐所有人都和我一般平庸了。」"},{"pid":"26f46bae53b32a9189364e6ff6314173a1f836a8","tid":1433421,"uid":202770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:39:51.000Z","msg":"臨訓之最後一推，希望呢首歌比到動力大家"},{"pid":"93e45e86f73a0a125a0580570f42a3da83de50a4","tid":1433421,"uid":235570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:41:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LHjxeJs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLHjxeJs.png&h=7cc87fdd&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8950830aa0b0d75c5e1579f1540d0905b27ade31","tid":1433421,"uid":98117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T23:55:45.000Z","msg":"晨早一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95191665561138ad92062b04b7e0179da5e7aaae","tid":1433421,"uid":98117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T23:56:10.000Z","msg":"真係好鍾意隻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7697d53da725cb617fb12490e890f0416f5ba84a","tid":1433421,"uid":202770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:07:22.000Z","msg":"大家早晨，繼續推"},{"pid":"881c68e9e691eb9daf0273ebdbbf9425b74995ce","t